  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I gave birth to a healthy child, and I-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I found out that a mohel and one rabbi are hidden in a-- not too far from us in a-- was like a-- a garden with trees.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they are somewhere-- there is some like-- like one little shed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In that shed, I can find him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this mohel happened [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] before this happened, he was-- their house was not too far where we were living.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went with a child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they [INAUDIBLE] there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I believed due to the fact I was always thinking maybe God will help me because I am so devoted to the Jewish tradition, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] but not fanatic, modern tradition, as up till now.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But now we became-- because we merged with a-- with an Orthodox synagogue.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But before was conservative.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then I have the baby.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't have no-- not sufficient milk or-- or anything what would give me, you know, milk.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I shall be able to provide natural from mother's breast to my baby.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I-- I asked my landlady, and I said, what shall I do?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What shall I do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where shall I get sugar?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she found out there-- as the Germans occupied us, the Germans including Banderas, Ukrainians, they robbed all the stores.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If anyone, any owner of the business could grab something to save in his pockets or-- or in his hands, then could be that this family [INAUDIBLE], which owned a pharmacy maybe they have saccharin or sugar, and they told me where they live in the house.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So this is why I went, and I got from them the saccharin.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
